viewData.name: ASUS 14" ZenBook Flip 14 UX461UA-DS51T Multi-Touch Laptop
viewData.short_description: Buy ASUS 14" ZenBook Flip 14 UX461UA-DS51T Multi-Touch Laptop featuring 1.6 GHz Intel Core i5-8250U Quad-Core, 8GB LPDDR3 | 256GB M.2 SSD 14" 1920 x 1080 Glossy Touchscreen. Review ASUS Flip 14
viewData.long_description: With a slate gray finish and a spin design, the ASUS 14" ZenBook Flip 14 UX461UA-DS51T Multi-Touch Laptop features a 14" display with a Full HD 1920 x 1080 resolution and a 16:9 aspect ratio, powered by integrated Intel HD Graphics 620. You can connect to an external display via the HDMI 1.4b output. The screen also has multi-touch support.
